We would like to be able to allocate "working days" ("original estimates") to a *release* (as we can now do with issues).  Then, it would be useful, in some views (roadmap, open issues) to display columns showing working time planned for a release and time currently planned for the issues of this release.  This could make it obvious that a release planned for some date already has too many issues assigned to it and that some issues need to be moved to later releases.

